name: Right Drawer Front Panel
Basic_description: Solid oak drawer face panel, approx. 30*16*1.8 cm, for the right-hand drawer.
Functional_description: Forms the visible front of the right drawer; supports the pull and provides hand contact to open/close.
Movement_description: Slides in and out of the console body on runners as a complete drawer assembly, guided by the face frame.
Grasped_description: Users grasp the pull or edges of this panel to operate the right drawer.
